title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 405: Featuring Joe Mullen
description:
On Episode 405 of Spittin’ Chiclets, the guys are joined by American Hockey Legend Joe Mullen. The three time Stanley Cup champion joined (12:22) the show to discuss growing up in NYC, playing in Calgary, playing in Pittsburgh and tons more. Murls also stopped by the show to talk all things EuroPuck, including the women’s world championships.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
